{"id": "pos049", "name": "Audio_Noah_702_11_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...... Aroma!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Hugs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sister...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I'm sorry...! I'm so sorry!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... <i>*Sniff*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You seem exhausted...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "A bit... I haven't slept well for the past few days...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "There are so many things I want to say to you...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah already told me quite a bit on our way here...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Is that so... Although I also have a lot of things I want to say to you personally, you should get some rest first. You must be dead tired... We can take our time with what we want to say after you wake up.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Okay. Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Noah, what is all this about?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I told her everything. Isn't this what you wanted?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Aroma... what did so say?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "She didn't blame us for what we did.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Even if she did feel that way, my guess is that she'll never actually say it to us. That's how kindhearted of a child she is.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, now that everything is out of the way, we now have the chance to let her forget all the pain. This time, we'll definitely succeed in turning her back into what she used to be.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Eh...? What do you mean...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Soon, we can go back to what we were before. I'll absolutely do the right thing this time.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah... wait a minute. What are you going to do? This isn't something you can decide on your own, is it?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No... Please hear me out first. This time, we aren't just simply resetting her brain. I just got the latest data from the stabilizers. Her brain is now in utter chaos...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Besides the conflicting sets of memories, there are even some parameters I've never seen before in her head now...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Parameters never seen before... I don't get it. What does that mean?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "It's difficult to explain. In short, these extra parameters are now strongly affecting her brainwaves. Perhaps it's due to her lengthy withdrawal from the stabilizers. The previously suppressed signals that shouldn't exist in Aroma's brain are starting to go berserk. This is also one of the sequelae I was most concerned about after the experiment was prematurely stopped. \n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "How come...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "If this keeps going on, her body... we both don't want to lose her again, right?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "But forcefully doing that experiment again... I don't know... if this is the right thing to do...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, trust me! This time, I won't make the same mistake again!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "That's not the problem. The original owner of that body...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I only care about Aroma. Everything else, I'll treat as the guilt I must shoulder for the rest of my life. I am prepared to face any consequences that may come with my actions.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I won't ask for anyone's forgiveness. I won't ask you to shoulder this guilt together with me either. Just treat it as a selfish decision I decided to pursue. Please, think about it carefully.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... I... I don't know. Give me some time. I can't make a decision right away...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Okay...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "抱きしめる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ごめんなさい……！ごめんなさい！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……うぅ……っ……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなた、とっても疲れた顔をしてる……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……最近あまり眠れなくて……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなたに話したいことがたくさんあるわ……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "車の中で、Noahさんに色々聞いた……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……そう……お姉ちゃんも話したいことはたくさんあるけれど、まずは休みなさい。\n疲れてるでしょう……\nあなたが目を覚ましてから、またゆっくり話しましょう。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん、ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Noah、これはどういうこと？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "全部、あの子に話したよ。\nこれが君の望んでいたことだろう？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aromaは……なんて？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの子は僕たちを責めるようなことは言わなかった。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……あの子のことだから、心では思っていても言えないのかも。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena、もう全て話したんだ。\nあの子を苦痛から解き放つチャンスだよ。\n今回は絶対に成功する。昔のあの子に戻せる。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……え……？意味が解らな……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "すぐに昔みたいに戻れるよ。\n今回は失敗したりしない。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……待ってちょうだい。\nあなた、何をするつもりなの？\nあなたの意思だけで決められる問題ではないでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや……まずは話を聞いてくれないか。\n今回はただリセットするだけじゃない。\nさっき安定器から最新のデータが取れたんだ。\n今のあの子の脳は極度な混乱状態にある……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "もつれた記憶だけじゃなくて、僕の見たことのないパラメーターが存在するんだ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "見たことのないパラメーター……何を言っているのか分からないわ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "なんて説明したらいいのかな……\nとにかく、それらの余分なパラメーターがあの子の脳波に強く影響を与えているんだ。\nもしかしたら、しばらく安定器を付けていなかったせいで、Aromaちゃんの脳内に存在するべきでないシグナルが暴走を始めたのかもしれない。\n実験を中断する上で心配だった後遺症の一つだよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そんな……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "このまま放っておけばあの子の身体は……\nもうあの子を失うの嫌だろう？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "でも、また強制的に実験を行うなんて……\n私、分からないの……これが正しいことなのか……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！僕を信じてくれ！\nもう失敗は繰り返さない！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そういう問題じゃない。\nあの身体の本来の持ち主の子は……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕が気にしているのはAromaちゃんのことだけだ。\n他のことに関しては、これから一生全ての罪悪感を背負って生きていく覚悟はできてる。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕は誰の許しも求めてない。\n君に僕と同じ罪を背負って生きてくれとも言わない。\n僕の独断だということにしてくれて構わないよ。\nお願いだ、よく考えてくれ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……私……私分からない……\n少し時間をちょうだい。\n今すぐ決めるのは無理……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あぁ……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "緊抱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對不起……！對不起！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳看起來累壞了……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……我這幾天都沒睡好……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我有好多話想對妳說……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 在路上已經說了很多了……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……這樣嗎……雖然我也有很多想說的，不過先去休息吧，妳一定很累了……等妳醒來我們再慢慢說。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Noah，這是怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我把一切都告訴她了，這不是妳要的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma 她……怎麼說？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她並沒有因此而責怪我們。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……就算有那樣的心情，我想她也說不出口的，她就是這樣的孩子。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，既然一切都說開了，現在就有機會讓她忘掉所有痛苦。這次一定會成功把她變回原本的樣子。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……咦……？什麼意思……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我們很快就又能像以前一樣了，這次我一定會做對。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……等一下，你要做什麼？這件事不是你說了算吧？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不……妳先聽我說，這次不是單純地重置這麼簡單了。我剛剛用穩壓器得出最新的數據了，她的大腦現在極其混亂……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "除了糾纏不清的記憶，甚至還存在著一部分我沒見過的參數……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "沒見過的參數……我聽不懂，什麼意思？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我很難解釋，總之那些多出來的參數現在正強烈地影響著她的腦波，也許是穩壓器移除太久，之前被壓抑住的那些不該存在於 Aroma 腦中的訊號開始暴走了，這也是中斷實驗後我最擔心的後遺症之一。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼會……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "這樣下去她的身體……我們都不想再次失去她了，對吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "但是強制再進行一次實驗……我不知道……這麼做是否是正確的……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，相信我！這次我不會再做錯了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不是那個問題，原本屬於那副身體的另一個……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我只關心 Aroma 的事，其他的就當成是我必須背負一輩子的罪惡感，我有這樣的覺悟。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我不強求任何人的原諒，也不強求妳與我一起背負這樣的罪孽，就當做是我一意孤行的決定，拜託妳好好想想了。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我……我不知道，給我一點時間吧，我沒辦法現在下決定……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......Aroma!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "꼭 껴안는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "미안해...! 언니가 미안해!!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......흐흑....\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": ".......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "흐흑... 왜 이렇게 혈색이 안 좋아 보여... 많이 피곤했지...?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응... 며칠 동안 잠을 못 자서...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네게 해주고 싶은 말이 너무 많아...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨가 오는 길에 이미 많은 것들을 말해줬어...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...그랬니...? 언니도 네게 할 말이 참 많은데... 우선 먼저 쉬어야겠구나. 엄청 힘들었을 텐데... 자고 일어나면 그때 다시 천천히 이야기해줄게...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응. 고마워, 언니.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "문이 닫힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......Noah, 대체 어떻게 된 일이야?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "말해줬어. 모든 것들을. 네가 바라던 거잖아?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...Aroma가... 뭐래?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "절대로 우리들을 탓하거나 그러진 않았어.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...설사 그러고 싶은 마음이 있다 하더라도 절대로 입 밖으로 꺼내지 못했을 거야... 걘 그런 아이거든...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, 이미 모든 것들을 털어놨어. 지금이 바로 저 아이가 짊어진 모든 고통을 지워줄 수 있는 기회야. 이번엔 확실히 저 아이를 원래 상태로 되돌릴 수 있어.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...뭐...? 그게 무슨 말이야...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "우린 곧 예전처럼 돌아갈 수 있어. 이번엔 무조건 해낼 거야.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah...? 잠깐만... 뭘 하려는 건데? 그 일은 이제 됐다고 하지 않았어?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니... 우선 내가 하는 말 끝까지 들어. 이번엔 단순한 리셋 작업이 아니야. 방금 안전 제어 장치로 최신 데이터를 뽑아냈는데, 저 아이의 뇌는 지금... 극도의 혼란을 보이고 있어...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "뒤얽혀 있는 기억뿐만 아니라 내가 본 적이 없던 일부 기억 파라미터까지 남아있었어...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "본 적이 없던 파라미터라니... 그게 무슨 말이야?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "설명하기 좀 어려워. 어쨌든 그 파라미터들이 지금 저 아이의 뇌파에 아주 강력하게 영향을 주고 있는 상황이야. 아마도 안정 제어 장치를 오랜 시간 착용하지 않아서 예전에 억제돼있던, Aroma 뇌에 남아있어서는 안 될 모종의 신호가 폭주해버린 거지. 이 현상은 실험 중단 이후로 내가 가장 염려하던 후유증 중에 하나이기도 해.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "어떻게 그런 일이...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이대로면 저 아이의 육체는... 우린 또다시 저 아이를 잃어선 안 돼. 내말 이해했어?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "하지만 또다시 강제적으로 실험을 강행하다가는... 나도 대체 뭐가 옳은 판단인지 감이 안 잡혀...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, 날 믿어! 이번엔 무조건 성공할 테니까!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그 문제가 아니야. 본래 저 육체의 주인이었던...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": [