心 Aroma 的事，其他的就當成是我必須背負一輩子的罪惡感，我有這樣的覺悟。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我不強求任何人的原諒，也不強求妳與我一起背負這樣的罪孽，就當做是我一意孤行的決定，拜託妳好好想想了。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我……我不知道，給我一點時間吧，我沒辦法現在下決定……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "紧抱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "对不起……！对不起！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……呜……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳看起来累坏了……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……我这几天都没睡好……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我有好多话想对妳說……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 在路上已经说了很多了……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……这样吗……虽然我也有很多想说的，不过先去休息吧，妳一定很累了……等妳醒来我们再慢慢说。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "关门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Noah，这是怎么回事？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我把一切都告诉她了，这不是妳要的吗？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma 她……怎么说？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她并没有因此而责怪我们。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……就算有那样的心情，我想她也说不出口的，她就是这样的孩子。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，既然一切都说开了，现在就有机会让她忘掉一切痛苦。这次一定会成功把她变回原本的样子。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……咦……？什么意思……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我们很快就又能像以前一样了，这次我一定会做对。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……等一下，你要做什么？这件事不是你说了算吧？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不……妳先听我说，这次不是单纯地重置这么简单了。我刚刚用稳压器得出最新的数据了，她的大脑现在极其混乱……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "除了纠缠不清的记忆，甚至还存在着一部分我没见过的参数……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "没见过的参数……我听不懂，什么意思？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我很难解释，总之那些多出来的参数现在正强烈地影响着她的脑波，也许是稳压器移除太久，之前被压抑住的那些不该存在于Aroma 脑中的讯号开始暴走了，这也是中断实验后我最担心的后遗症之一。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎么会……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "这样下去她的身体……我们都不想再次失去她了，对吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "但是强制再进行一次实验……我不知道……这么做是否是正确的……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，相信我！这次我不会再做错了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不是那个问题，原本属于那副身体的另一个……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我只关心 Aroma 的事，其他的就当成是我必须背负一辈子的罪恶感，我有这样的觉悟。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我不强求任何人的原谅，也不强求妳与我一起背负这样的罪孽，就当做是我一意孤行的决定，拜托妳好好想想了。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我……我不知道，给我一点时间吧，我没办法现在下决定……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}